===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la}} '''[[adamantem]]''', accusative singular form of '''[[adamas]]''' "hard as steel", from {{etyl|grc}} < '''{{polytonic|[[ἀδάμας]]}}''' (adamas) "invincible", from '''{{polytonic|[[ἀ-]]}}''' (a-) "not" + '''{{polytonic|[[δαμάζω]]}}''' (damazo) "I tame".

